data.description: PRICE REDUCED 01/20This R2 zoned home is move in ready and provides a tranquil space with the potential of an ADU or Casita for the front of the home w/ alley access. No drywall or particleboard here. This home was built to last with premium framing and lathe and plaster construction. All doors are premium wood veneer including the three pocket doors found in the kitchen area. Attractive mid-level real wood paneling in kitchen and office, original oak flooring. Refurbished cabinets, stainless steel KitchenAide appliances an extra wide range and matching premium stainless steel vent. Kitchen includes a double lazy Susan corner cabinet for all your canned goods. The kitchen also includes an extremely rare vented cabinet to help extend the life of your vegetables and dry goods. The large living room offers plenty of space for a family gathering but can also be a place of quiet relaxation while you enjoy the classic wood burning fireplace and garden views through the expansive picture window. The 'man cave' office offers a wall of closet and cabinet space. On this home you will find a brass mail slot where your mail is delivered right into the office! Physical updates to the home include copper piping, updated electrical hardware and panel, laminate flooring in living room hallway and bedrooms, new water heater in 2022, and premium grade fence on south side of home. The garage has an epoxy floor great for a classic!
